description:
Underlying and extended data for: Increase of SARS-CoV-2 RNA load in faecal samples prompts for rethinking of SARS-CoV-2 biology and COVID-19 epidemiology. It consists of: 


	  UnderlyingData.zip  -&nbsp;Mass spectrometry dataset (one file in MGF format), as described in Petrillo, M. et al.&nbsp;Increase of SARS-CoV-2 RNA load in faecal samples prompts for rethinking of SARS-CoV-2 biology and&nbsp;COVID-19 epidemiology. 
	  ExtendedData.zip  - Supplementary material (two&nbsp;files in PDF format), as described in Petrillo, M. et al.&nbsp;Increase of SARS-CoV-2 RNA load in faecal samples prompts for rethinking of SARS-CoV-2 biology and&nbsp;COVID-19 epidemiology,&nbsp;

